#

Lemon Tahini Sauce

5 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Sesame

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

SauceCondimentVegan

Description

A creamy, tangy sauce that elevates any dish with its zesty flavor.

Ingredients

  • tahini: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • garlic clove, minced: 1
  • water: 2-4 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
